Name: X-linked Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 1
Definition: An Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in an X-linked recessive mutation of EMD on chromosome Xq28.

Name: autosomal dominant Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 2
Definition: An Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in an autosomal dominant mutation of LMNA on chromosome 1q22.

Name: autosomal recessive Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 3

Name: autosomal dominant Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 4
Definition: An Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in an autosomal dominant mutation of SYNE1 on chromosome 6q25.2.

Name: autosomal dominant Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 5
Definition: An Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in an autosomal dominant mutation of SYNE2 on chromosome 14q23.2.

Name: X-linked Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 6
Definition: An Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in an X-linked recessive mutation of FHL1 on chromosome Xq26.3.

Name: autosomal dominant Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy 7
